: \"the speed\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they did not seem to think that affected the race, which again, confused me, because I thought we were saying that if you come in the sprint is lane, that's it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprint\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Kordi said he wasn't angry with Carlin for how he raced, and said he's a worthy bronze medalist, he added he did not think the jury would be so forgiving if it was another sprinter.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3270, \"end\": 3275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kordi_Shirazi\", \"score\": 0.9999998860093976, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kordi\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kordi_Shirazi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kordi_Shirazi\"}, {\"begin\": 3302, \"end\": 3308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"score\": 0.9999999940723683, \"rank\": 5.927673003113625e-09, \"text\": \"Carlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a worthy bronze medalist\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3365}, {\"ngram\": \"the jury\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"another sprinter\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I accepted the decision, and just want to move on,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think what it's encouraging is people pushing boundaries.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"boundaries\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a saying in sports that you swallow your whistle in the highest sort of pressurized moments, meaning they are not going to give the call because it's such a grand occasion.\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a saying\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"your whistle\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3633}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest sort\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3653}, {\"ngram\": \"pressurized moments\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3676}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3721}, {\"ngram\": \"such a grand occasion\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope that wasn't the case, but I still am confused with all the warnings and head butting and coming out the line he was doing yesterday and today, that it did not actually come of anything.\\\"\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 3777, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"all the warnings\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3832}, {\"ngram\": \"head butting\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3849}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3873}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3941, \"to\": 3949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The boos and the protests did not hurt Carlin as much as the entire sprint tournament, where he had to defeat riders like Nicholas Paul (Trinidad & Tobago) and Ota all while just getting over a fractured ankle that he suffered in April.\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 4189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3992, \"end\": 3998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"score\": 0.9999999940723683, \"rank\": 5.927673003113625e-09, \"text\": \"Carlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\"}, {\"begin\": 4075, \"end\": 4083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou